---
description: Testing policy and minimum expectations
alwaysApply: true
---

- Unit test utility logic in `src/lib`.
- Integration test route behavior where relevant.
- Add e2e tests for user-critical flows.
- Do not merge failing tests.
- Report coverage for changed files when available, or mark `n/a` with reason.
- Performance validation should be production-mode first (`npm run build` + `npm run start`); use dev mode only for smoke checks.
